{"tid":304002,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"(半live)帶你走進不一樣的日本東北","createTime":"2017-06-30T14:44:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-21T05:22:18.000Z","uid":116764,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"04cca2ab37abb77322f72c06ee62234c93700707","tid":304002,"uid":116764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T14:44:10.000Z","msg":"小弟去過日本都唔少次<br />\n今次去嘅地方相信唔少人都未聽過<br />\n等我開心share下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nDay1<br />\n坐red eye 飛過去都幾難頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/30/223641_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F30%2F223641_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=1b0b5033&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/30/223710_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F30%2F223710_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=fc43abfc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c2127ee5c51d889f511a89634e65d750a7cf8ed4","tid":304002,"uid":104837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T14:47:48.000Z","msg":"支持東北遊記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e70464e444b453789c1dad57e4ba7af92ddeb435","tid":304002,"uid":26232,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T14:51:23.000Z","msg":"上個禮拜去完<br />\n不過支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n東北冬天先多人去"},{"pid":"b8e30768257b2ab874b7050021d88e768a0867ed","tid":304002,"uid":116764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T14:52:05.000Z","msg":"Day1 continue <br />\n換好pass諗住坐hayabusa 直去八戶，點知東京去仙台full哂book唔到。唯有咁去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86cfca435ee0141f2214029ee8879a450bb5ca93","tid":304002,"uid":26232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T14:52:50.000Z","msg":"巴打住邊度？"},{"pid":"c8096b8c86606c444d9032b3b3f6a9b89efb895b","tid":304002,"uid":116764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T14:59:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Day1 continue <br />\n換好pass諗住坐hayabusa 直去八戶，點知東京去仙台full哂book唔到。唯有咁去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n自膠㩒錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/30/225258_26da3397092bc52ae8d70277664325ff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F30%2F225258_26da3397092bc52ae8d70277664325ff.jpg&h=e130ef3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今日行程好簡單行種差海岸 東北自然步道<br />\n唔知點解平日黎架假日限定特急，估唔到東記都有特見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/30/225531_0e9cf524af44e16e803f0339d0f495c5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F30%2F225531_0e9cf524af44e16e803f0339d0f495c5.jpg&h=de6cb960&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n種差海岸<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/30/225702_aab94631ede706e2c4d28a21c520d5a4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F30%2F225702_aab94631ede706e2c4d28a21c520d5a4.jpg&h=7fae8dfa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/30/225703_7a2f28fc9f996f5f08504754b0e7bdc2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F30%2F225703_7a2f28fc9f996f5f08504754b0e7bdc2.jpg&h=675d24a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蕪島<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/30/225731_46818b87aff7807abe16d47748363ed9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F30%2F225731_46818b87aff7807abe16d47748363ed9.jpg&h=8e842bd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n行完返酒店check in 今次住本八戶因為可以影火車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/30/225841_c6f5f1418f938fe21d191d6155294ded.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F30%2F225841_c6f5f1418f938fe21d191d6155294ded.jpg&h=b10657e2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"37549aefd9d60a0c07b9e123b05fc43bdee958d1","tid":304002,"uid":116764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T14:59:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上個禮拜去完<br />\n不過支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n東北冬天先多人去</blockquote><br />\n冬天成日受天氣影響好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3737bfcb03a1b46d453da337594a76f6361a518","tid":304002,"uid":116764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T15:00:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打住邊度？</blockquote><br />\n宜家係北上"},{"pid":"40dfb4b241bbeba45dd45376598dfe8a4574769b","tid":304002,"uid":116764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T15:06:56.000Z","msg":"Day 2 <br />\n今日八戶出發去久慈目的係為咗潮聖<br />\n如果有睇開日劇嘅朋友都應該知道小海女<br />\n我今日嘅目的就係衝着佢而來<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/30/230349_2e2a18aba800a3c03aa20cd9cd8f4982.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F30%2F230349_2e2a18aba800a3c03aa20cd9cd8f4982.jpg&h=521d10dc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/30/230351_ec13fda8c75d7ebd2c4c63ca47ddca30.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F30%2F230351_ec13fda8c75d7ebd2c4c63ca47ddca30.jpg&h=c9e5f37e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/30/230353_98250ded3cc21c41a9e2348d16bcf4c8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F30%2F230353_98250ded3cc21c41a9e2348d16bcf4c8.jpg&h=8fc1a5d3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/30/230357_4a3c245ee71cf13d14928b33f1263780.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F30%2F230357_4a3c245ee71cf13d14928b33f1263780.jpg&h=69a4c737&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原來都幾冷清，冇乜人去<br />\n小海女poster<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/30/230518_21acb73772229baab825a7955b3382d8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F30%2F230518_21acb73772229baab825a7955b3382d8.jpg&h=1a47155a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/30/230544_0859759fbba6d5e7ed5de59e2d6026f1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F30%2F230544_0859759fbba6d5e7ed5de59e2d6026f1.jpg&h=5b8ede0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n百貨公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/30/230651_9e6216018759d2eb8f2be10f5ede9166.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F30%2F230651_9e6216018759d2eb8f2be10f5ede9166.jpg&h=14bfd8f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n三陸鐵道<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/30/230619_e5273e8b085b6f222fa53b15356aad70.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F30%2F230619_e5273e8b085b6f222fa53b15356aad70.jpg&h=38ac477c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bb051b1a5a7967612a787e431d01151481c23bf8","tid":304002,"uid":11896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T15:13:28.000Z","msg":"岩岩去完日本，好想再去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a75cbc03d331aa332eaa5b16e7bbe9b3b046cf6e","tid":304002,"uid":49868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T15:13:58.000Z","msg":"你見到個架藍色特別車叫Resort Umineko，星期六、日先會有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n來往八戶到久慈"},{"pid":"3341a21082ab02e29a2a1f3facc52459aac6ea5e","tid":304002,"uid":116764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T15:19:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你見到個架藍色特別車叫Resort Umineko，星期六、日先會有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n來往八戶到久慈</blockquote><br />\n我知<br />\n重點我去嗰日係星期二<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1de4798aa3940faa0e4d6193790454b49382bf7","tid":304002,"uid":49868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T15:26:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你見到個架藍色特別車叫Resort Umineko，星期六、日先會有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n來往八戶到久慈</blockquote><br />\n我知<br />\n重點我去嗰日係星期二<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61cf210ddc139297799a3a7949267f52ad6248f2","tid":304002,"uid":34692,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T15:29:27.000Z","msg":"全個連登得你一個去過日本東北？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9c6695cfd8775ab337d8db7c3b61514137d3665","tid":304002,"uid":116764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T22:48:38.000Z","msg":"Day 3 <br />\n今日check out 南下經盛岡去宫古<br />\n你可能會問點解唔係久慈坐三陸鐵道去<br />\n因為我唔想日日換酒店<br />\n同埋之後有地方想去都係新幹線沿線<br />\n山田線盛岡去宫古班次少得可憐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咪有坐巴士去<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/01/064333_5ccede2b1079e827c968b1cace9f44ff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F01%2F064333_5ccede2b1079e827c968b1cace9f44ff.jpg&h=5df5d216&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/01/064355_d3d9d74e70a6b0436dd1d7700d563bb7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F01%2F064355_d3d9d74e70a6b0436dd1d7700d563bb7.jpg&h=8078ff37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n宫古站<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/01/064423_14d12fba59943b6dd105035a2db35cc1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F01%2F064423_14d12fba59943b6dd105035a2db35cc1.jpg&h=a21f7591&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n淨土之浜係主要今日想去嘅地方<br />\n我覺得佢比松島靚<br />\n少好多旅客多返D寧靜<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/01/064621_f1bf4d253b4f303e5029b9e9ddc19c20.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F01%2F064621_f1bf4d253b4f303e5029b9e9ddc19c20.jpg&h=a1ad4f03&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/01/064623_ef787f8b3b8f5d51760846448d93b065.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F01%2F064623_ef787f8b3b8f5d51760846448d93b065.jpg&h=7b04ad0e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/01/064624_f48fc19533f535669b1ecc54d9ce702c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F01%2F064624_f48fc19533f535669b1ecc54d9ce702c.jpg&h=f6243ecc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/01/064625_e9fc22c0afe58312266d59bfc19049d4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F01%2F064625_e9fc22c0afe58312266d59bfc19049d4.jpg&h=ec5b5f91&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/01/064626_948f2f6157281b91b0fba48d149bfeb3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F01%2F064626_948f2f6157281b91b0fba48d149bfeb3.jpg&h=039d75e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最後坐巴士返盛岡轉落北上check in<br />\n呢間酒店嘅特別就係可以睇新幹線<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/01/064831_f350f09f1ee5c64e3614452de03fdad2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F01%2F064831_f350f09f1ee5c64e3614452de03fdad2.jpg&h=ccae8362&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b4051c02549a9e4c03acecf5b18df63bc295e2cf","tid":304002,"uid":116764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T23:04:35.000Z","msg":"Day 4 <br />\n今日主要去311重災區<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/01/065227_068269c63f714fda464fc67fc1693757.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F01%2F065227_068269c63f714fda464fc67fc1693757.jpg&h=ead6c54a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBRT（其實係假，99％行國道）成日delay <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/01/065357_12ac7234e9fbf500153cbd44b35e7d17.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F01%2F065357_12ac7234e9fbf500153cbd44b35e7d17.jpg&h=4f869b81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今日第一站去奇蹟一本松<br />\n以前呢到係一片好大嘅松樹林，但海嘯沖淨一棵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢唯一嘅一棵標誌着當地居民嘅希望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我見日本人去到個個都好sad眼濕濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/01/065733_933b913c935ae9077b6b5cec1871bb00.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F01%2F065733_933b913c935ae9077b6b5cec1871bb00.jpg&h=603ecc1f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/01/065734_2252766123c9e6c348a679414252386e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F01%2F065734_2252766123c9e6c348a679414252386e.jpg&h=8c81fd24&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/01/065736_8b016ef08a681fccf0a33cb1ebc4827a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F01%2F065736_8b016ef08a681fccf0a33cb1ebc4827a.jpg&h=720816e9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/01/065738_6d54ab0d43da0b30ece9a10db72aad6b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F01%2F065738_6d54ab0d43da0b30ece9a10db72aad6b.jpg&h=2169ccbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原本國道休息站 <br />\n每一件留低係到嘅海嘯遺跡都經過當地居民投票已決定留低，目的只係想警惕世人海嘯所帶來嘅禍害<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/01/065817_3068833b03d4fc890c912ee4342e7caa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F01%2F065817_3068833b03d4fc890c912ee4342e7caa.jpg&h=632c130f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後去南三陸町<br />\n眼前原本係南三陸町最繁華嘅地段，因為海嘯而將佢完全摧毁<br />\n宜家努力重建中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/01/070243_3c37e26cbf788f0d2933c9e363770b84.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F01%2F070243_3c37e26cbf788f0d2933c9e363770b84.jpg&h=2fcb1ec7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n復興商店街<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/01/070323_d99842893bb2d6275af0250a3b7cbe40.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F01%2F070323_d99842893bb2d6275af0250a3b7cbe40.jpg&h=becc10e2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/01/070325_bf3646a224ec4027a40d7401a9eaef1d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F01%2F070325_bf3646a224ec4027a40d7401a9eaef1d.jpg&h=f9074f0b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"28f9ba043b07cf704230529f4ecae404208754cb","tid":304002,"uid":77864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T04:10:40.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n剛剛去完東北21日 有好多地方趕唔切去/無直接車去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87cbc67d787a052efcc444171d6fe7c8029cc828","tid":304002,"uid":116764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T10:12:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n剛剛去完東北21日 有好多地方趕唔切去/無直接車去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n東北好多地方都好值得去，但交通班次太少<br />\n有時一日去得一到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b04b988d62523015418ee443093edf0d8ad01ddd","tid":304002,"uid":26232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T11:17:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n剛剛去完東北21日 有好多地方趕唔切去/無直接車去<img src=\"/a